    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1903-09-01T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1903-09-01T00:00:00-05:00" n="179"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d179">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Beaupré</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">United States Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Bogotá</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1903-09-01">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 1, 1903</hi>
                        </date>.<lb/>(Received through German embassy September 5.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Have not received Department’s messages, while others of late date for various
                    legations have-arrived. I have sent important telegrams 30 and 31. On receiving,
                    answer by German minister.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Beaupré.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
